data.description: Nestled in the Sun City golf course Retirement community, this Ranch Style Home captivates with laminate wood floors, a unique color scheme, & ceiling fans. The kitchen shines with granite counters, a tiled backsplash, and chic white wood cabinets. Enjoy two spacious bedrooms, ample storage, an interior laundry room, and a well-appointed bathroom. The adaptable Arizona Room and well-maintained desert landscape with a covered patio enhance outdoor living. The backyard features block fencing, a double gate with extra cement. Residents can access nearby amenities like a heated pool, spa, and clubhouse. Conveniently located near premier facilities such as Great Golf Courses, Banner Del Webb Hospital, Aqua Fitness Club, Frys Grocery Store, and Sun City Sun Bowl Outdoor Concerts!
